      "category": "Industry",
      "description": "In this post, we introduce the UI for optimized generative AI inference recommendations in Amazon SageMaker AI Studio, a low-code no-code (LCNC) experience. The API already gives you programmatic access to recommendations, but it assumes you know which parameters to set and how to interpret raw benchmark output. The UI removes that assumption. It guides you through preset use-case profiles, visual comparisons of results, and one-click deployment, so teams without deep infrastructure expertise...",
